18
00:00:12,582 --> 00:00:15,582
http://hiqve.com/

19
00:00:18,606 --> 00:00:20,399
<i>Brothers reunited!</i>

20
00:00:20,441 --> 00:00:24,111
<i>Darth Maul, the sinister Sith
thought to have been destroyed</i>

21
00:00:24,195 --> 00:00:27,782
<i>so many years ago
by Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi,</i>

22
00:00:28,074 --> 00:00:31,744
<i>was found alive
by his brother, Savage Opress,</i>

23
00:00:31,827 --> 00:00:34,830
<i>and taken back to Mother Talzin
on Dathomir.</i>

24
00:00:35,414 --> 00:00:38,668
<i>Though Darth Maul's memory
has yet to be fully restored,</i>

25
00:00:38,751 --> 00:00:43,506
<i>his need for vengeance has awakened,
more powerful than ever.</i>

26
00:00:46,551 --> 00:00:49,971
Patience, brother. We're almost home.

27
00:00:56,394 --> 00:01:00,398
Far above, far above,
we don't know where we'll fall.

28
00:01:00,898 --> 00:01:05,236
Far above, far above,
what once was great is rendered small.

29
00:01:27,675 --> 00:01:30,636
-Brother...
-Kenobi... Kenobi...

30
00:01:31,012 --> 00:01:32,763
Brother, we have to go.

31
00:01:33,347 --> 00:01:36,642
Kenobi... Kenobi...

32
00:01:39,687 --> 00:01:41,606
Fine. Stay here.

33
00:02:19,769 --> 00:02:21,562
Savage.

34
00:02:26,025 --> 00:02:27,401
Mother.

35
00:02:28,110 --> 00:02:30,071
Shall we?

36
00:02:30,279 --> 00:02:34,575
What happened here?
Where are the rest of the sisters?

37
00:02:34,950 --> 00:02:39,330
Dooku sent his minions to destroy us,

38
00:02:39,413 --> 00:02:41,916
but we will survive.

39
00:02:42,249 --> 00:02:44,293
We always have.

40
00:02:45,753 --> 00:02:49,757
You found him. I knew you would.

41
00:02:50,216 --> 00:02:53,594
Yes. He is damaged.

42
00:02:54,095 --> 00:02:56,889
He doesn't remember much of his old life.

43
00:02:59,058 --> 00:03:02,937
Hmm. But he does remember something.

44
00:03:04,021 --> 00:03:07,316
Something or someone named Kenobi.

45
00:03:07,942 --> 00:03:09,735
It is an obsession.

46
00:03:18,452 --> 00:03:22,456
Come, let us fix what has been broken.

47
00:03:24,917 --> 00:03:27,086
Come to me.

48
00:03:27,128 --> 00:03:29,171
Come to me.

49
00:03:29,463 --> 00:03:33,801
Follow us, son of Dathomir.

50
00:03:33,884 --> 00:03:37,054
Follow me, lost one.

51
00:03:37,138 --> 00:03:40,599
Come, child of Dathomir.

52
00:03:41,976 --> 00:03:44,103
Follow me.

53
00:04:15,926 --> 00:04:18,262
Now sleep.

54
00:04:29,523 --> 00:04:30,816
Now what?

55
00:04:30,858 --> 00:04:33,444
Now we begin.

56
00:06:10,291 --> 00:06:17,131
Arise, Maul, reborn son of Dathomir.

57
00:06:18,799 --> 00:06:20,050
Brother?

58
00:06:28,475 --> 00:06:30,144
Brother.

59
00:06:42,865 --> 00:06:45,367
My... My legs.

60
00:06:50,998 --> 00:06:54,251
They have been restored by Mother Talzin.

61
00:06:55,044 --> 00:06:59,882
It has been so long
and my path has been so dark,

62
00:07:00,633 --> 00:07:03,344
darker than I ever dreamed it could be.

63
00:07:03,594 --> 00:07:05,512
And yet you survived.

64
00:07:19,568 --> 00:07:21,570
Of course I survived.

65
00:07:43,926 --> 00:07:48,055
My hatred kept my spirit intact
even though my body was not.

66
00:07:48,847 --> 00:07:51,475
Yet I was lost and became a rabid animal

67
00:07:51,558 --> 00:07:54,645
and such is how you found me, brother.

68
00:07:54,728 --> 00:07:57,272
Discarded, forgotten.

69
00:07:58,857 --> 00:08:01,402
I have missed so much.

70
00:08:02,236 --> 00:08:05,739
The Force feels out of balance.

71
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:11,078
Yes. There is conflict. The Clone Wars.

72
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:15,749
Oh, yes. So it began without me.

73
00:08:16,542 --> 00:08:18,752
You can begin again, brother.

74
00:08:27,928 --> 00:08:33,017
I was apprentice to the most
powerful being in the galaxy once.

75
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:37,146
I was destined to become so much more,

76
00:08:37,855 --> 00:08:41,442
but I was robbed of that destiny
by the Jedi,

77
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:44,194
by Obi-Wan Kenobi.

78
00:08:44,361 --> 00:08:47,948
Then you must have your revenge,
my brother.

79
00:08:48,657 --> 00:08:52,494
Yes, we shall start with revenge.

80
00:09:05,299 --> 00:09:07,968
The supply ship's here. Go on ahead.

81
00:09:23,108 --> 00:09:26,111
Brother, what are we doing here?

82
00:09:26,487 --> 00:09:29,656
The Jedi won't be out this far in the galaxy.

83
00:09:29,782 --> 00:09:31,867
In a galaxy at war, Savage,

84
00:09:31,950 --> 00:09:35,829
there is only one way
to get the attention of the Jedi.

85
00:09:39,875 --> 00:09:43,003
Slaughter of the innocent,

86
00:09:43,128 --> 00:09:46,090
mercilessly and without compromise.

87
00:09:54,723 --> 00:09:59,019
<i>There will be more innocent blood
on your hands, Kenobi,</i>

88
00:09:59,103 --> 00:10:02,439
<i>unless you come here, face me.</i>

89
00:10:03,190 --> 00:10:07,694
<i>Come alone and if you do not, this world</i>

90
00:10:10,447 --> 00:10:11,865
<i>will burn.</i>

91
00:10:12,407 --> 00:10:13,909
I have to go.

92
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:17,329
Not alone you're not.
We'll send a task force with you.

93
00:10:17,579 --> 00:10:20,040
No, you see what he's capable of.

94
00:10:20,124 --> 00:10:23,001
He's a broken, unbalanced monster.

95
00:10:23,043 --> 00:10:25,921
I've dealt with him before. I can do it again.

96
00:10:26,130 --> 00:10:28,757
I disagree. This is clearly a trap.

97
00:10:29,508 --> 00:10:33,512
Against my better judgment,
agree with Master Kenobi, I do.

98
00:10:34,596 --> 00:10:37,724
Finish what he started long ago,
Obi-Wan must.

99
00:10:39,518 --> 00:10:41,311
I'm off to Raydonia.

100
00:10:42,729 --> 00:10:45,899
Master Yoda, if this is indeed Darth Maul,

101
00:10:45,983 --> 00:10:49,903
his capture is far too important
to leave it to Obi-Wan alone.

102
00:10:50,362 --> 00:10:51,405
Mmm.

103
00:10:51,864 --> 00:10:53,866
Not alone will Kenobi be,

104
00:10:54,741 --> 00:10:57,035
an unexpected ally he may have.

105
00:10:59,621 --> 00:11:02,374
Trust the Force, we must.

106
00:11:11,091 --> 00:11:12,926
Sure, sure. Coming up.

107
00:11:13,010 --> 00:11:16,388
Hey, bounty hunters,
stop monopolizing all of the transmitters.

108
00:11:16,430 --> 00:11:18,098
Shut off your speaker, droid!

109
00:11:19,892 --> 00:11:22,186
These marks are too easy.

110
00:11:23,061 --> 00:11:25,105
Not enough credits.

111
00:11:25,230 --> 00:11:26,440
Whoa!

112
00:11:26,523 --> 00:11:30,694
A million credits!
Who is this Savage Opress?

113
00:11:30,944 --> 00:11:31,987
I'll take it!

114
00:11:32,070 --> 00:11:35,032
Don't even consider it, boys.

115
00:11:36,783 --> 00:11:38,577
I've got this one.

116
00:12:56,029 --> 00:12:57,030
Jedi.

117
00:12:58,365 --> 00:13:00,742
I have been waiting for you.

118
00:13:01,868 --> 00:13:04,204
I'm not sure I've made your acquaintance.

119
00:13:04,538 --> 00:13:08,875
I am surprised you could have
forgotten me so easily

120
00:13:08,917 --> 00:13:14,131
after I killed your master
and you left me for dead on Naboo.

121
00:13:15,007 --> 00:13:16,466
It is you.

122
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:21,596
You may have forgotten me,
but I will never forget you.

123
00:13:22,139 --> 00:13:27,102
You cannot imagine the depths
I would go to to stay alive,

124
00:13:27,477 --> 00:13:32,065
fueled by my singular hatred for you.

125
00:13:32,649 --> 00:13:36,903
That may be so, but I defeated you before,
and I can defeat you again.

126
00:13:40,365 --> 00:13:42,909
Don't be so certain.

127
00:13:44,161 --> 00:13:45,245
You?

128
00:15:08,995 --> 00:15:11,415
Still as weak as ever.

129
00:15:15,627 --> 00:15:18,130
And they call you, "Master."

130
00:15:19,005 --> 00:15:24,177
You know, when I cut you in half,
I should have aimed for your neck instead.

131
00:16:04,384 --> 00:16:06,386
Anything more to say?

132
00:16:06,803 --> 00:16:09,890
I like your new legs.
They make you look taller.

133
00:16:16,229 --> 00:16:18,565
I will make sure
you stay awake long enough

134
00:16:18,607 --> 00:16:21,568
to feel every single cut.

135
00:16:21,610 --> 00:16:26,072
Your death will be beyond excruciating.

136
00:16:26,364 --> 00:16:30,911
You will suffer as I have suffered!

137
00:16:40,962 --> 00:16:43,048
What a surprise.

138
00:16:44,424 --> 00:16:48,261
My former servant, still an animal.

139
00:16:48,512 --> 00:16:50,430
And you have a friend now.

140
00:16:50,514 --> 00:16:51,890
My brother.

141
00:16:52,015 --> 00:16:53,558
A brother?

142
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:56,937
Looks like he's half the man
you are, Savage.

143
00:16:57,521 --> 00:16:59,064
How unfortunate.

144
00:16:59,147 --> 00:17:00,941
I was looking for a challenge,

145
00:17:01,024 --> 00:17:04,569
not some wretched castoffs
from the Night brothers clan.

146
00:17:04,611 --> 00:17:07,030
What a disappointment.

147
00:17:08,698 --> 00:17:10,283
Who is this, brother?

148
00:17:10,325 --> 00:17:13,787
A Dathomir witch. She betrayed me.

149
00:17:15,872 --> 00:17:18,959
She knows too much, destroy her.

150
00:17:34,474 --> 00:17:38,478
Kenobi, don't tell me someone's
finally knocked the fight out of you.

151
00:17:38,603 --> 00:17:39,813
Wake up!

152
00:17:43,483 --> 00:17:44,651
Ventress?

153
00:17:44,734 --> 00:17:47,362
It looks like I'm here to rescue you.

154
00:17:47,821 --> 00:17:49,656
When did you become the good guy?

155
00:17:49,739 --> 00:17:51,491
Don't insult me.

156
00:17:52,075 --> 00:17:54,828
Oh ! What a lovely sight to wake up to.

157
00:17:54,911 --> 00:17:56,454
Don't flatter yourself, Kenobi,

158
00:17:56,496 --> 00:18:00,083
you've never been much to look at,
especially now.

159
00:18:00,375 --> 00:18:02,752
The witch and the Jedi.

160
00:18:05,046 --> 00:18:07,549
Here for our taking.

161
00:18:13,013 --> 00:18:14,514
I want that back.

162
00:18:14,639 --> 00:18:17,183
That's fine, red's not my color.

163
00:18:18,602 --> 00:18:19,728
Ready?

164
00:18:19,811 --> 00:18:21,896
Like you even have to ask.

165
00:19:09,736 --> 00:19:11,321
Ventress, catch!

166
00:19:33,551 --> 00:19:36,137
Your master, Qui-Gon Jinn,

167
00:19:36,221 --> 00:19:39,724
I gutted him
while you stood helpless and watched.

168
00:19:39,808 --> 00:19:43,186
How did that make you feel, Obi-Wan?

169
00:19:51,778 --> 00:19:53,988
Your rage has unbalanced you.

170
00:19:54,447 --> 00:19:57,325
That is not the Jedi way, is it?

171
00:20:09,129 --> 00:20:11,840
-We're outmatched.
-You want to run?

172
00:20:11,965 --> 00:20:13,341
I learned from watching you.

173
00:20:13,425 --> 00:20:15,802
Funny. The cockpit?

174
00:20:17,470 --> 00:20:18,555
Now!

175
00:20:26,730 --> 00:20:28,356
Come on, come on!

176
00:20:37,365 --> 00:20:40,410
-Hurry, Kenobi !
-I'm working on it!

177
00:20:44,789 --> 00:20:46,124
Come on, hurry!

178
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:49,502
Now would be a good time!

179
00:20:49,711 --> 00:20:50,879
Blast!

180
00:21:12,358 --> 00:21:15,862
That was cutting it a little close.

181
00:21:16,196 --> 00:21:18,031
You do know, it's not over.

182
00:21:18,156 --> 00:21:19,199
I know.

183
00:21:19,282 --> 00:21:21,534
They'll be after us both now.

184
00:21:27,874 --> 00:21:30,794
What now, brother?
Do we go after them?

185
00:21:31,544 --> 00:21:35,507
No. We will be patient, Savage.

186
00:21:36,132 --> 00:21:39,886
I've waited so many years for my revenge,

187
00:21:40,386 --> 00:21:42,555
I can wait a little longer.

188
00:21:42,972 --> 00:21:45,975
But the Jedi will know
that you have survived.

189
00:21:46,142 --> 00:21:48,269
They will be coming for us.

190
00:21:51,606 --> 00:21:53,733
I am counting on it.

191
00:21:53,757 --> 00:21:58,757
http://hiqve.com/

